		<b>Comment By mandy, 11-03-06</b>
		<p>I wish just once these mailings would include a simple list of what the candidates actually support. That being said - I am *really* enjoying the Angie Paccione vs. Marilyn Musgrave ad war. It gets more entertaining every passing day.</p>
		
		<b>Comment By Bob Wire, 11-03-06</b>
		<p>Thanks for the laughs this morning, Jenny. As a graphic designer, I can relateâ€”I've even coined a term for us artists who occasionally must abandon our esthetic in favor of filthy lucre: whoretists.<br />
I laid out a brochure for a candidate for Missoula's City Council a few years back, and he called several times to tell me about all the compliments he received on it. He won the election by three votes, and turned out to be a mean-spirited, conservative prick. After that I decided that I'd better pay closer attention to who my clients are!</p>
		
